250
00:10:31,244 --> 00:10:33,045
electromagnetic separation,

251
00:10:33,045 --> 00:10:35,123
and liquid thermal diffusion.

252
00:10:35,123 --> 00:10:37,896
After testing these 4 different technologies,

253
00:10:37,896 --> 00:10:41,045
